Entries.default: "You want something, Cathŵenna's the one to speak to."
"Frankly, I wanted to keep shooting arrows at you."
"There are another twenty of us among the trees, all with bows trained at your heart."
"I'd tell you to watch yourself, but we're already watching you."
"You want something, Cathŵenna's the one to speak to."
"Thanks for the coin. We'll make it count."
"Turns out you're not half as bad as you look."
"Maybe someone would've helped us earlier if we hadn't shot arrows at everything that moved..."
